======================================================================
To install:
======================================================================

make

======================================================================
To run:
======================================================================
simply give
./mcmc

to see the corner plot of the MCMC chains give
python plot_corner.py
open cornerplot.pdf

to see the best-fit model against the data, give
python plot_model.py

to see the actual chains give
python plot_chains.py

======================================================================
For documentation
======================================================================
cd docs/html
open index.html
